,"tid":325943,"uid":8222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T09:40:51.000Z","msg":"有d女人仲嘈過細路<br />\n成場係咁問問問<br />\n啤幾次都唔識收聲<br />\n係要人屌"},{"pid":"0e8702b71846b2847d127e7607c06f795acfabc3","tid":325943,"uid":65376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:35:38.000Z","msg":"試過開聲大大聲屌班生番既老母"},{"pid":"94e52154f63edc7679b822c343d32a3e53ed9274","tid":325943,"uid":48918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:37:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該攞膠紙封撚實d細路把口先俾佢哋入場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n綁撚埋對腳呀 <br />\n踢踢踢"},{"pid":"4855048c6fb2169e57ea52c8c4650ebc85a1fa6c","tid":325943,"uid":15592,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:43:55.000Z","msg":"當年入戲院睇斷背山，見到兩個師奶各帶一個5、6歲左右既細路去睇，入場時我已經心諗做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n到中段d hehe戲肉時，見到嗰兩個師奶坐立不安，走又唔係，繼續睇又唔知點同個細路解釋咁，我真係由心咁恥笑左出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55b041ccb81f02693415c9988c7809a7e22a5805","tid":325943,"uid":21255,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T10:48:07.000Z","msg":"成日都話<br />\n你生得細路<br />\n你開心你既事<br />\n其他人冇義務為左既開心承擔責任<br />\n<br />\n你有自由帶小朋友去娛樂場所、帶佢地去旅行<br />\n但你冇權俾你個小朋友對其他人造成滋擾<br />\n<br />\n唔撚識教唔撚好生<br />\n<br />\n每次搭飛機都有細路喊<br />\n每次睇戲都有細路鳩叫<br />\n搭親巴士都俾佢地嘈<br />\n<br />\n唔撚識教射返落牆啦屌你老母<br />\n諗起就嬲"},{"pid":"3ba56e916cef2486492d98c53270513211ff4909","tid":325943,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:21:55.000Z","msg":"仲有 手機 響<br />\n<br />\n明明睇戲要 關機/較靜音<br />\n<br />\n但次次都有手機響<br />\nD人仲要接電話:「喂........我家陣唔得閒, 睇緊戲呀.......好......我睇完再打比你啦」"},{"pid":"85993181122f320cdf89f004a37f19845306c46d","tid":325943,"uid":187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-18T13:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個細個未比過屋企人帶去睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個個細路都嘈架啦 係咪連街都唔出得？</blockquote><br />\n你係咪覺得個世界要老馮忍鳩一個三唔識七既細路？<br />\n有乜咁巴閉呀你老味"},{"pid":"831146857cda0db714909af16f088595d3ac930e","tid":325943,"uid":128215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:09:15.000Z","msg":"試過有細路成套戲問左不下50次點解 <br />\n燥到冇心機睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"184438288cb262caa71ef7b4770d03dd8d84ddd7","tid":325943,"uid":122167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"最撚憎遇著 d 細路, 嘈到仆街"},{"pid":"298aa48dc5a9832b92313bfe2ec561b06724624b","tid":325943,"uid":67346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T09:57:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Diu手指粗 撳錯負評添</blockquote><br />\n屌我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唯有留言正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f92f5a84814c6e135b12db4f36b4d404e07821ef","tid":325943,"uid":6397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-19T12:44:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e0296b767bc5900aefeb5cf6d368f2be60e3a60","tid":325943,"uid":52936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:12:30.000Z","msg":"唔識教就戴返個套啦仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe96029b0bbc9870fda12375801ccd74350a98d3","tid":325943,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:15:07.000Z","msg":"屌即刻正評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"060dab093afd8ccfff260bf9a49989e0afe21b76","tid":325943,"uid":122211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:17:03.000Z","msg":"睇戲同搭飛機都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"423593c0370c45c0a0d539236cfc255c758eefcd","tid":325943,"uid":81177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:21:44.000Z","msg":"上次坐飛機後面有兩個細路玩張餐枱由上機玩到落機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />震到呢"},{"pid":"9b9aab789efb7f29e0b713dc27683308e64cd5f5","tid":325943,"uid":106623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:33:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>見到咁多正評都估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"7da73e71cc1aab6bdf396ac60235f7a664133068","tid":325943,"uid":75365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T03:38:28.000Z","msg":"屌 嘈撚到仆街"},{"pid":"4eb7aeb464590c0640b19cf273b92c7e6ee72f6c","tid":325943,"uid":93217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:13:40.000Z","msg":"Ching hoball，未入嚟已經估到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a2b94bfcbfb1c9f39785a2fb88c1f663e7aebf","tid":325943,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:21:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲有 手機 響<br />\n<br />\n明明睇戲要 關機/較靜音<br />\n<br />\n但次次都有手機響<br />\nD人仲要接電話:「喂........我家陣唔得閒, 睇緊戲呀.......好......我睇完再打比你啦」</blockquote><br />\n呢啲都算叫識收，有啲廢老真係會講成分鐘都唔收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e547bbbbb256e9181679dcd16bb836d841d0377","tid":325943,"uid":90692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:24:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有邊個細個未比過屋企人帶去睇戲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  個個細路都嘈架啦 係咪連街都唔出得？</blockquote><br />\n屌，出街一定要睇戲？細路一定嘈？點解日本細路咁靜？"},{"pid":"4f8cf7f01f0cd510f781820f38d537337d44e498","tid":325943,"uid":127347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T04:27:02.000Z","msg":"正評，小朋友又唔明劇情講乜，又嘈住晒，又係咁踢人椅背<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ed3